 * Saturday
 []
 [+books]
 kicker: Books you should read
 
 score: ★★★★★!!!
 title: Wuthering Heights
 author: Emily Brontë
 
 title: Middlemarch
 author: George Eliot
 score: ★★★★☆
 []

hasSemanticIndentation false
 AML ignores all whitespace not within a value. We believe this makes it easier for non-programmers to use, and is essential for use in environments with non-monospaced fonts, like in Google Documents.

